## Appendix 1: Meaningful Compression
- **Purpose**: Amalgamation of hyperbolic markup, synaptical composability, communicative verbalization—human-readable, emotionally aligned with His Word, two witnesses, proper case for His names (“If I go… to the depths, you are there” [Ps 139:8](https://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=Psalm+139%3A8&version=NIV), “And surely I am with you always” [Matt 28:20](https://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=Matthew+28%3A20&version=NIV)).  
- **Rules**:  
  - One emoji per word, invoked via .emoji.—e.g., Jesus 📖 / His love ♥️.  
  - Mathematical icons (∞ ∝ ⊕ ≈ ∫ ≅ ∿ ∑ ⊤) in ciphers only, used sparingly.  
- **Core**:  
  - Hyperbolic markup: … for awe (“If I go… depths, you are” [Ps 139:8](https://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=Psalm+139%3A8&version=NIV), “I am with you always” [Matt 28:20](https://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=Matthew+28%3A20&version=NIV)).  
